import {Router, Route, Routes} from 'react-router-dom'
import { Dashboard } from '../pages/Dashboard/Dashboard'



export const UnAthorized = ()=>{
    return(<>

        <Routes>
            <Route path='/' element={<Dashboard/>}></Route>
            <Route path='/dashboard'  element={<Dashboard/>}></Route>
            <Route path='*'  element={<Dashboard/>}></Route>
        </Routes>
    
    </>)
}
